<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Doesn't really matter.</i></font>

160
00:10:32,770 --> 00:10:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He was always something of a busybody.</i></font>

161
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:36,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Got a group of friends</i></font>

162
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:39,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and they operated something that 
resembled a school for swordsmanship...</i></font>

163
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:44,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But a hunt went bad, and his 
entire gang was wiped out.</i></font>

164
00:10:55,630 --> 00:10:59,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Long story short, he couldn't make 
ends meet as a Brave after that.</i></font>

165
00:11:01,150 --> 00:11:07,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>These days, he trains combatants for the 
Dark Overlord, the Coffin Count of Storms.</i></font>

166
00:11:07,190 --> 00:11:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oversees them, too.</i></font>

167
00:11:11,710 --> 00:11:14,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They number around a hundred.</i></font>

168
00:11:14,510 --> 00:11:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The majority of them are kids from
around town with no place better to go.</i></font>

169
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:24,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Some ran away from home,</i></font>

170
00:11:24,560 --> 00:11:27,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>some couldn't stay with their 
parents or within the system,</i></font>

171
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:30,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>some are foreigners 
who couldn't return home...</i></font>

172
00:11:30,260 --> 00:11:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>or their kids.</i></font>

173
00:11:38,170 --> 00:11:41,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And he's looking after kids like this?</font>

174
00:11:41,180 --> 00:11:43,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are we <i>sure</i> he's a bad guy?</font>

175
00:11:43,530 --> 00:11:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dude stole a panda corpse.</font>

176
00:11:45,630 --> 00:11:49,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A panda?! He's an absolute monster, then!</font>

177
00:11:49,180 --> 00:11:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And good at running away, too.</font>

178
00:11:53,870 --> 00:11:59,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Best way to get any intel is gonna 
be taking one of his people alive.</font>

179
00:11:59,020 --> 00:12:01,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The money is pretty appealing, too.</font>

180
00:12:04,070 --> 00:12:09,080
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#f1f1f1"><b><font size="28">Scum of the Brave</font></b></font></font></font>

181
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's make this as nonlethal as we can.</font>

182
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:25,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got it.</font>

183
00:12:42,590 --> 00:12:44,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">None of you are a match for him.</font>

184
00:12:44,650 --> 00:12:45,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fall back!</font>

185
00:13:13,930 --> 00:13:15,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you all to back off, damn it!</font>

186
00:13:16,060 --> 00:13:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who gave him E3?!</font>

187
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:20,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're abandoning this place!</font>

188
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:22,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Scatter! Now!</font>

189
00:13:27,180 --> 00:13:29,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're kinda overprotective,</font>

190
00:13:29,490 --> 00:13:33,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">considering I only came 
by to have a little chat.</font>

191
00:13:33,430 --> 00:13:35,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could've been a bit 
more amicable about it.</font>

192
00:13:39,640 --> 00:13:42,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no idea what 
happened to the Musician.</font>

193
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:44,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wasn't he a deviant serial killer?</font>

194
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:48,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With no shortage of vendettas, I'd wager.</font>

195
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:49,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Agreed.</font>

196
00:13:56,850 --> 00:14:00,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he was trying to learn about E4.</font>

197
00:14:02,920 --> 00:14:05,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That monster you cooked up...</font>

198
00:14:06,450 --> 00:14:08,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you used some of it to make him, right?</font>

199
00:14:11,010 --> 00:14:15,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is the Coffin Count of Storms 
the one distributing E4?</font>

200
00:14:18,310 --> 00:14:21,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're sorely mistaken.</font>

201
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:25,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've been trying to figure out 
what that concoction is ourselves.</font>

202
00:14:25,730 --> 00:14:30,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do I know <i>you're</i> not working 
for the Half Dragon yourself?</font>

203
00:14:31,700 --> 00:14:34,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because, maybe, I'm trying to kill them?</font>

204
00:14:38,720 --> 00:14:41,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're a bit like arms dealers.</font>

205
00:14:43,660 --> 00:14:48,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They provide E4 and E3 procured from 
illicit sources to weaker Dark Lords</font>

206
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:51,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in an attempt to disrupt the status quo.</font>

207
00:14:51,660 --> 00:14:57,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They provoke conflict between the
Dark Lords to boost their own business.</font>

208
00:14:58,520 --> 00:15:00,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some real warlords, huh?</font>

209
00:15:00,950 --> 00:15:02,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And who's running the show?</font>

210
00:15:02,420 --> 00:15:04,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Couldn't tell you.</font>

211
00:15:04,130 --> 00:15:06,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But they're our enemy, in any case.</font>

212
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:09,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My personal goal is for stability.</font>

213
00:15:09,810 --> 00:15:14,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want a powerful Dark Lord, such as the
Coffin Count of Storms, to reign over all.</font>

214
00:15:15,180 --> 00:15:19,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their business is an obstacle
for that goal.</font>

215
00:15:19,640 --> 00:15:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe we can work together,
in regards to the Half Dragon.</font>

216
00:15:25,520 --> 00:15:27,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Work together, my ass.</font>

217
00:15:27,940 --> 00:15:30,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're asking for a lot, after 
all the times you've tried to kidnap me.</font>

218
00:15:32,100 --> 00:15:33,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey there.</font>

219
00:15:34,420 --> 00:15:38,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll save the rest of my 
questions for your big brain.</font>

220
00:15:42,650 --> 00:15:46,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Especially since we've got a 
big old bounty here with us.</font>

221
00:15:47,590 --> 00:15:52,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coach. I won't let them take Yoshi-kun.</font>

222
00:15:52,210 --> 00:15:53,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter the cost.</font>

223
00:15:53,970 --> 00:15:57,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It won't come to that. I swear.</font>

224
00:15:58,070 --> 00:16:01,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yashiro the Reaper! Malta the Mole!</font>

225
00:16:01,280 --> 00:16:02,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For the sake of my minions,</font>

226
00:16:02,810 --> 00:16:04,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you two will perish here!</font>

227
00:16:50,110 --> 00:16:51,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not bad.</font>

228
00:17:20,310 --> 00:17:22,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Settle down, now.</font>

229
00:17:23,280 --> 00:17:26,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You ran from your old man, right?</font>

230
00:17:26,130 --> 00:17:27,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get what that's like.</font>

231
00:17:27,690 --> 00:17:32,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I was little, mine made 
me fight boars and bears...</font>

232
00:17:32,480 --> 00:17:34,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Talk about a nightmare.</font>

233
00:17:34,840 --> 00:17:37,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can always run again, 
after we send you back.</font>

234
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:40,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're old enough to manage that.</font>

235
00:17:40,610 --> 00:17:42,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Things will work out.</font>

236
00:17:44,130 --> 00:17:45,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Help...</font>

237
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:48,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coach, please save me!</font>

238
00:17:48,660 --> 00:17:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to go back to that house!</font>

239
00:18:15,580 --> 00:18:17,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't want him talking, huh?</font>

240
00:18:17,320 --> 00:18:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You just blew a huge bounty for me, man.</font>

241
00:18:19,240 --> 00:18:21,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think I'm silencing him?</font>

242
00:18:23,480 --> 00:18:26,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Neither of them ever
wanted to return home.</font>

243
00:18:26,640 --> 00:18:28,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's that simple.</font>

244
00:18:29,340 --> 00:18:33,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I made a promise that, if it ever looked 
like they were going to be dragged back,</font>

245
00:18:33,530 --> 00:18:35,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would kill them myself.</font>

246
00:18:36,410 --> 00:18:40,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I granted a sword for those who 
had to do battle with fear.</font>

247
00:18:40,970 --> 00:18:45,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I provided a life of dignity to children 
for whom there was no other salvation!</font>

248
00:18:45,970 --> 00:18:50,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What bullshit. And that's the job you 
think is fancier than being a Brave?</font>

249
00:18:50,480 --> 00:18:52,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What else could I do?!</font>

250
00:18:52,730 --> 00:18:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Being a Brave is no different 
than being an executioner.</font>

251
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:59,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How convenient it must be
for the masses...</font>

252
00:19:00,760 --> 00:19:03,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Letting us filthy outcasts 
clash amongst ourselves,</font>

253
00:19:03,020 --> 00:19:04,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">wiping each other out!</font>

254
00:19:05,370 --> 00:19:07,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what awaits you!</font>

255
00:19:07,840 --> 00:19:09,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will lose everything!</font>

256
00:19:33,980 --> 00:19:37,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He can control other
people's gloves, too?!</i></font>

257
00:20:17,570 --> 00:20:20,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Malta. I underestimated him.</font>

258
00:20:22,810 --> 00:20:25,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kinda feel bad for them.</font>

259
00:20:25,910 --> 00:20:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

260
00:20:32,410 --> 00:20:34,920
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#15171e">Harumi</font></b></font></font></font>

